'''克萊森特'''（{{lang|en|'''Clay Center'''}}）為[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[克莱县_(堪薩斯州)|克莱县]]的一座城市，也是克莱县的[[县城|縣治]]所在地<ref name="GR6">{{cite web|url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|accessdate=2011-06-07|title=Find a County|publisher=National Association of Counties|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQozzgAf?url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有4,334人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web |title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |accessdate=2011-03-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table |archivedate=2011-07-21 }}</ref>。

==歷史==
克萊森特於1862年開始有人定居<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA361#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Embracing Events, Institutions, Industries, Counties, Cities, Towns, Prominent Persons, Etc. | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=361 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-date=2014-09-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920123651/http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA361#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。城市名稱為因坐落於克萊縣的地理中心而得名<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA160#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=160 | access-date=2016-07-09 | archive-date=2014-09-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922195333/http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA160#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

克萊森特境內首間郵政局於1862年7月3日成立<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CY |title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 (archived) |publisher=Kansas Historical Society |accessdate=2014-06-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009130019/http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county%3ACY |archivedate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。

克萊森特有[[芝加哥，岩島和太平洋鐵路|芝加哥，岩島和太平洋鐵路]]和[[聯合太平洋鐵路|聯合太平洋鐵路]]的支線通過<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.kgs.ku.edu/General/Geology/Clay/03_geog.html | title=Geohydrology of Clay County | publisher=Kansas Geological Survey | accessdate=2014-08-02 | archive-date=2019-10-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023183152/http://www.kgs.ku.edu/General/Geology/Clay/03_geog.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==地理==
克萊森特坐落在北緯39度22分48秒、西經97度7分23秒（亦可表示為39.379920, -97.123168）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|3.08|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，全境皆為陸地<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。克萊森特所在的地理位置正好位於[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]和[[纽约|纽约]]等兩大城市之間。從克萊森特到這兩座城市皆相距{{convert|1224|mi|km}}<ref>{{cite web | title = "As The Crow Flies" Distance Calculator | publisher = Tjpeiffer | url = http://tjpeiffer.com/crowflies.html | accessdate = July 2014 | archive-date = 2017-10-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171004064346/http://tjpeiffer.com/crowflies.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===氣候===
夏季溼熱、冬季不甚乾冷為此地區的氣候特徵。根據[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]，克萊森特的氣候屬於[[副热带湿润气候|副热带湿润气候]]，在氣候圖中簡寫「Cfa」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=955141&cityname=Clay+Center%2C+Kansas%2C+United+States+of+America&units= |title=Climate Summary for Clay Center, Kansas |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020031237/https://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=955141&cityname=Clay+Center%2C+Kansas%2C+United+States+of+America&units= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

